flowchart TD
    U[User] --> CF[Amazon CloudFront]
    CF --> WAF[AWS WAF]
    WAF --> COG[Amazon Cognito]
    COG --> APIGW[Amazon API Gateway]
    APIGW --> L[AWS Lambda]
    L --> BR[Amazon Bedrock]
    L --> DDB[Amazon DynamoDB]

    WAF --> LOGS[WAF Logs]
    LOGS --> S3[Amazon S3]
    S3 --> ATH[Amazon Athena]
    ATH --> QS[Amazon QuickSight]
